---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Affiliate Disclosure — Trove Collections" topDisclosure={false}>
  <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Trove Collections, LLC participates in affiliate marketing programs. Here is
    how that works, in plain English.
  </p>

  <h2>What this means</h2>
  <p>
    Some of the product links on this site are affiliate links. If you click one
    of those links and make a purchase, Trove Collections may earn a commission,
    depending on the retailer or affiliate program. The price you pay is the
    same either way. You are not charged extra for buying through our link.
  </p>

  <h2>Our recommendation standard</h2>
  <p>
    We only feature items that we, or someone in our trusted curator circle,
    have personally used, purchased, received, tested, or would confidently
    give as a gift. Editorial integrity is the point of this site. We do not
    feature an item solely because it may generate a commission. If a product
    is popular but no one in our circle has actual experience with it or a
    sufficient basis to recommend it, it does not appear here.
  </p>

  <h2>Affiliate programs we participate in</h2>
  <p>
    We are part of, or in the application process with, affiliate networks and
    brand-direct programs, which may include Amazon Associates, ShareASale,
    Awin, Rakuten Advertising, Commission Junction (CJ), Impact, Sephora, Ulta,
    UGG, Etsy, Adagio Teas, Korin, Novica, TirTir, and others.
  </p>
  <p>
    As an Amazon Associate, Trove Collections earns from qualifying purchases.
  </p>
  <p>
    Where a link goes to a retailer or program in which we are not enrolled, no
    commission is earned. We may still link to that retailer because the
    recommendation is independent of whether a commission is available.
  </p>

  <h2>What we will not do</h2>
  <p>
    We will not write fake reviews. We will not knowingly make false or
    misleading statements about a product. We will not change a recommendation
    based solely on which program pays more. If we believe a product is not
    right for a particular use case, we will say so. If our view of a product
    changes, we may update or remove the recommendation.
  </p>

  <h2>FTC compliance</h2>
  <p>
    Trove Collections discloses affiliate relationships in accordance with the
    FTC's Endorsement Guides, 16 CFR Part 255. Our goal is for affiliate
    disclosures to be clear, conspicuous, and easy to understand. Short
    affiliate disclosures appear on pages containing affiliate links, and this
    page provides additional detail about how our affiliate relationships work.
  </p>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>
    Email us at <a href="mailto:hello@trovecollections.com">hello@trovecollections.com</a>.
    We try to respond to messages within a day or two, subject to travel and
    availability.
  </p>

  <p class="muted" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
    <em>Last updated: May 2026. Trove Collections, LLC is a limited liability
    company organized in the United States.</em>
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .lede {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }
  p { max-width: 65ch; }
</style>
